channel.title: Give me ideas for tracks to make
channel.description: I’m currently in class on the verge of breaking down because my life is falling apart. Music has always helped me deal with that. So please, give me any ideas you can think of for song starters. Just like a genre, a theme, anything, really. I just want to distract myself, and this might help.
